inputs.remark: V1 speech audiometry出现了PTA和SRT的结果互换

logic_summary: The remark states that PTA and SRT results are swapped in V1 speech audiometry. However, in the provided JSON, the values for PTA (in Pure-tone audiometry) and SRT (in Speech audiometry) are identical: Right=8 dB HL and Left=12 dB HL. Therefore, swapping them results in no change. The values are also consistent with the pure-tone thresholds (5-10 dB) and the description of hearing being slightly poorer in the left ear.
